ingredients.ingredient: ¼ pound breakfast sausage, fully cooked and crumbled
½ cup shredded Cheddar-Monterey Jack cheese blend

gear.name: small oven-safe skillet or air fryer egg bake dish

cookingTips: Cook sausage completely before adding to frittata; partially cooked sausage won't cook through
Use a non-stick or well-oiled skillet to prevent sticking
Whisk eggs gently to avoid incorporating too much air, which can create large holes
enrichment.coachingPrompt: Guide me through crumbling cooked sausage, beating eggs with cheese and vegetables, pouring into a skillet, and air frying until set and fluffy.
